      "body" : "-1: The <code>n</code>th item of any <code>Iterable</code> is easily well-defined. When working with a <code>List</code>, you have additional guarantees that the operation is stable (and can often be performed in O(1) time), but it doesn&#39;t change the definition of the <code>n</code>th item of an <code>Iterable</code>."
