      "body" : "For those (still) arriving here: I think jheddings&#39; answer is probably the best &quot;get it done&quot; answer, though I&#39;d prefer @DonaldRaab&#39;s (way down the page) for cases where I&#39;m already using the GC library.  My answer is really for the case where one may want to write in flexibility for later (say, if one decides that the <i>second</i> element is the new hotness)."
