    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In java 8:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Optional&lt;String&gt; firstElement = collection.stream().findFirst();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>For older versions of java, there is a getFirst method in Guava <a href=\"https://google.github.io/guava/releases/21.0/api/docs/com/google/common/collect/Iterables.html#getFirst-java.lang.Iterable-T-\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Iterables</a>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Iterables.getFirst(iterable, defaultValue)\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
